• Develop Robotic Process Automations with UiPath/AA/Blueprism;
• Identify and create reusable automation components;
• Develop customizations utilizing .Net and third party APIs;
• Implement Bot throughput logging, auditing, and exception handling;
• Support User Acceptance Testing with business and IT.

Required Experience And Skills
• Bachelor’s degree in IT, Software engineering or a related field.
• 2+ years of professional experience in to IT
• Must have experience in Object oriented programming with Microsoft .Net (VB and C#) or VBA, Java, C#, IIS, JavaScript, RPA.
• Familiar or certified with UiPath, Blue prism or AA.
• Familiarity with web service interaction (REST/SOAP);
• Excellent communication skills with ability to manage multiple priorities
• Ability to work on own and in a team-oriented environment

Desired Skills and Experience
Auditing, C#, C++, HTML, Information Technology, Java, JavaScript, MySQL, Process Automation, Software Development, SQL, Software developing... UAT, customization, Microsoft .NET, scopes of work
